{
  "title": "Tangy Irish Pork Roast",
  "description": "A juicy, tangy pork back ribs roast with a flavorful tadka (tempering) for a energizing Irish-inspired dish. Perfectly balanced with tangy spices and aromatic herbs.",
  "cuisine": "irish",
